<h2>Online Help for M B/L BUYING Object</h2>
<br></br>
This is an Object to manage costs for one container(MB/L shipment). <br></br>
These costs are eventually allocated to relevant H B/L based on the cargo volume.<br></br>
In case of Consolidation Box, there are 4 shared costs in M B/L Buying<br></br>
<ul>
1. Partner Cost allocation<br></br>
2. Warehouse Cost Allocation(example, Devanning Charge)<br></br>
3. Carrier Cost Allocation(example, CY charge and other Surcharges)<br></br>
4. Carrier Cost Allocation(TAX)(example, DOC Fee)<br></br>
</ul>
<br></br>
To allocate the costs to linked H B/L Selling/Buying automatically, below two conditions must be met.<br></br>
<ul>
1. COST ALLOCATION CATEGORY must be selected in MBL BUYING Object.<br></br>
2. COST ALLOCATION CATEGORY must be selected in H B/L Selling/Buying Object.<br></br>
3. Selected data must be the same between 1 and 2.<br></br>
</ul>
<br></br>


